data.description: Fall in love from the curb. Custom brick home located in highly desired Spring Creek Oaks. The BEST location in SCO. Property sits adjacent to neighborhood park, backs to walking trails, w/ short stroll to Kuehnle Elementary. Improvements include 2 HVAC systems (2023 & 2018), storm impact windows (2020), whole home surge protection (2019), electrical panel w/ 200 amp (2021). 2 story entry w/ wood floors, formal dining & private office. Island kitchen is open to family room w/ great counter space & stainless appliances. Family room w/ built-ins, stone fireplace, plantation shutters & tons of natural light overlooking an oasis style backyard w/ sparkling swimming pool. Primary suite w/ crown molding. En-suite bath w/ dual sinks, walk-in shower & jetted tub. Game room & extra media space. Spacious guest bedrooms w/ great closet space. Detached 3 car garage, porte cochere & wrought iron driveway gate. SCO amenities- 2 clubhouses, pools, tennis courts, pickleball, baseball & soccer fields.
